snippet.title: So I played Star Defenders (Eric Gurt's new game)
snippet.description:
This video was finished on 31 January 2021. Has to be delayed due to a copyright claim and audio issue.
[Yeah, I can monetize video now thanks to my younger brother Psycho Foxy (Danish)] - Ghost Dan/Zombie Killer (Daniel)

Ex Dee

This video shows the older version. Maybe I should record it again? Idk, probably not.

Play it here!
https://www.gevanni.com:3000/
The game is made by the creator of Plazma Burst 2, Eric Gurt.

Eric Gurt's twitter announcing the game.
https://twitter.com/Eric_Gurt/status/1352373945887039496

Special thanks to Avre for making me notice this game.
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCdDgSMh-8SrqsZNtvfYU9ew

Music
Super Bomberman R - Planet Bomber (World 7)
Super Bomberman R - Planet Technopolis (World 1)
Touhou 6: Embodiment of Scarlet Devil - Un Owen Was Her?
Earthbound - Sanctuary Guardian
Sonic 3 - Doomsday Zone (OC Remix)
Deltarune - Scarlet Forest [by Toby Fox]
Deltarune - Legend [by Toby Fox]

Yes, I will change my name to Ghost Dan. I will announce it later.
======================================================
If you enjoy the video, why not LIKE the video. But If you want more, feel free to subscribe and also, have a nice day ^^

Check out our alternate/singular channel!! It has several different content.
Zombie Killer: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCP6ZNN1A6_Na_4qlXa8EF5g
Psycho Bonnie: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC4iEW-b3m0lqfFhP_79N2hg
Psycho Foxy: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8HEx_czfu3fwW89SFPR1vA
